    <item>
      <title>英国工党暂停候选人资格，因其对自身不利进行投注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-s-labour-suspends-candidate-for-betting-against-himself</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国主要反对党工党暂停了一位在即将举行的大选前对自己进行押注的候选人的资格，这是有关选举押注的最新争议，此前此类押注仅困扰着里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/uk-s-labour-suspends-candidate-for-betting-against-himself</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国主要政党在电视辩论中就经济、移民问题发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/france-s-main-parties-clash-on-economy-immigration-in-tv-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国三大政治党派的领导人首次电视辩论中就退休、税收和移民等各个问题发生冲突，他们试图让选民相信他们值得信任，可以管理欧洲第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/france-s-main-parties-clash-on-economy-immigration-in-tv-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京访朝后朝鲜试射弹道导弹展示武力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-in-a-show-of-force-after-putin-s-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜发射一枚疑似弹道导弹，但似乎在飞行中失败，这是朝鲜试图展示武力的举动，大约一周前，朝鲜与俄罗斯达成军事协议，引起美国及其盟友的震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-in-a-show-of-force-after-putin-s-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 21:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
